{"tid":1857833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"呢個時候仲唔爭取加入俄羅斯聯邦仲等幾時？","createTime":"2020-02-02T11:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T17:42:49.000Z","uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"82c0435884e999b107e02fc79fac584ecfe1e274","tid":1857833,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯宣佈派軍隊去疫區撤僑，林鄭又特登咩都唔做等香港變疫區，呢個時候仲唔係機會叫俄羅斯入黎做人道援助，脫中入俄？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bN7sOA7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbN7sOA7.jpg&h=51479833&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDJfXus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDJfXus.jpg&h=ede69a68&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">脫中入俄，唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1a8e75e1a3b45bd3f916bfc3f3e7a65d942ebf5d","tid":1857833,"uid":295548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"《天滅中共賦》<br />\n<br />\n共黨臣民 作惡多端<br />\n外侵諸邦 內屠義士<br />\n赤匪所至 寸草不生<br />\n禍國殃民 血債累累<br />\n習妖維尼 逆天而行<br />\n自立為帝 天怒人怨<br />\n庚子伊始 天譴將臨<br />\n大仙報夢 國運已盡<br />\n共黨治下 必有七患<br />\n正月武肺 播毒中原<br />\n二月流感 飛禽盡亡<br />\n三月地震 血流成河<br />\n四月豬瘟 百物騰升<br />\n五月飢荒 易子而食<br />\n六月內戰 析骸而爨<br />\n七月水災 長江決堤<br />\n炎共將亡 水德當立<br />\n歲在庚子 天滅中共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCW3BCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCW3BCS.jpg&h=64a71671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14b2ee8efb3ee2bd350ac1bd5eb7b8943a0b8844","tid":1857833,"uid":127929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:02:24.000Z","msg":"人黎, 餵樓主食藥"},{"pid":"b3260aa1bf4f318b584925013e196badc9b7e7ed","tid":1857833,"uid":146030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:03:54.000Z","msg":"樓主崇完俄未"},{"pid":"b48f734d0f73b58732a51a1540e574711390a80f","tid":1857833,"uid":12